text: Þis earon þara manna noman þe gewritene earon from bynsincgtune to readanoran in<../images/tbar.gif>bisceoprice to uueogerna cestre mid heara teame & mid þy tudre þe from him cume a on ece yrfewardnysse.
Alhmund, Tidulf, Tidheh, Lull, Lull, Eaduulf.
Hoc autem rus his finibus ambitur.
Æt byrhtan wellan from teolulfes treowe ondlong longan hylles on fildena weg þonan on holandene up on cadandune to æðelheges gemære.

Þonan to ecgfriðes gemære þonne a big ecgfriðes gemære to cuces hæma gemære<../images/tbar.gif>to incghæma gemære<../images/tbar.gif>swa ondlong incghæma gemære suð þurh east leh<../images/tbar.gif>to gisles bæce<../images/tbar.gif>ondlong gisles bæce<../images/tbar.gif>eft to ceolwulfes treowe.
And<../images/tbar.gif>mæð lond be betweonum egsafordam & strætforda be norðan broce & þone wudu þærto þe scylfhrycg is haten.
